snippet.title: Symphony X - Evolution(The Grand Design) (Cover by SoniKhaos)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Symmetric Chaos Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SymmetricChaos

Patrick asked me.
"Do you like Symphony X? Do you know any songs from them?”
I said, thinking of my childhood singing their songs in a karaoke room.
"Yes, I used to sing Evolution often."
“Wait a second.”
He hadn't said anything for several hours, then suddenly appeared and sent me an almost complete backing track.
“Would you like to sing on it?”
but I wasn’t good enough to sing this song though patrick told me he liked it.

As time passed, recently I was making various attempts by recording a lot of songs with him.
One day, while practicing singing as usual, I suddenly remembered this song, so I recorded it and sent it to Patrick.
“So it’s time to play my guitar again to match your voice.”

After eight years since we started the song, finally, the song came to light again with a whole new level of elements.

Special Thanks To Alex Nasla

Symphony X - Evolution(The Grand Design) (Cover by SoniKhaos)

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Vocals, Mixing, Mastering, Video Editing 
Patrick Fallang (Symmetric Chaos, Norway) - Guitars, Drums, Music Arrangement, Premixing
Alex Nasla (Symmetric Chaos, US) - Keyboards

#RusselAllen #EpicMetal
